flowchart TD
    A[User presses Run proof lane] --> B[GUI starts fixed standalone streamCodexCommandWithControl]
    B --> C[Output READY arrives]
    C --> D[Surface becomes awaitingWrite]
    D --> E[User sends raw stdin]
    E --> F[Output PING arrives]
    F --> G[Surface becomes awaitingTerminate]
